<h3>Test Results</h3>
<p><strong>Prompt used:</strong> "Create a REST API endpoint for user authentication with JWT tokens, including login, register, and token refresh routes in a Node.js/Express app"</p>
<ul>
<li>Code quality: 9.5/10 — clean, well-structured output</li>
<li>Generation time: ~8 seconds</li>
<li>Multi-file accuracy: 9.5/10 — correctly wired across files</li>
<li>Bug-free on first run: 9/10</li>
<li>Context awareness: 9.5/10 — understood project structure</li>
</ul>

